Fix https://github.com/etcd-io/etcd/issues/20793

Verified the fix using [upgradeDemo](https://github.com/ahrtr/etcd-issues/tree/master/etcd/upgradeDemo) with config below. 

```
{
  "clusterSize": 3,
  "upgradePath": [
    {
      "version": "v3.5.19",
      "path": "/usr/local/bin/etcd-v3.5.19"
    },
    {
      "version": "v3.5.21",
      "path": "path-to-etcd-release-3.5/bin"
    },
    {
      "version": "v3.6.4",
      "path": "/usr/local/bin/etcd-v3.6.4"
    }
  ]
}
```

Before this PR, roughly can reproduce about 2 times on every 5 tries.

With patch in this PR, no reproduction at all.

I thought about integrating [upgradeDemo](https://github.com/ahrtr/etcd-issues/tree/master/etcd/upgradeDemo) into our pipeline, but it may need some effort. We can discuss it separately for main branch only.  For stable releases, we suggest to keep it as it's, as we won't add any new features in stable releases.

cc @fuweid @ivanvc @jmhbnz @serathius @siyuanfoundation @spzala 


